genresAdvancedInfo.name: orquesta tropical
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Orquesta Tropical is a genre of music that originated in the Caribbean and Latin America. It is characterized by the use of traditional instruments such as the conga, bongo, and timbales, as well as brass and wind instruments.
